snippet.title: Amber Heard Sent Topless Photos To Johnny Depp
snippet.description: Amber Heard Sent Topless Photos To Johnny Depp - Pervy hackers struck again Sunday, this time leaking a cache of X-rated photos and video of Johnny Depp’s fiancée Amber Heard.More than 50 explicit images stolen from model Amber Heard popped up on the Internet sites 4Chan and Reddit.The pilfered videos show the 28-year-old blond Texan, whose mother is an Internet researcher, participating in an apparent threesome and smoking what looks like a bong
